Name: Duck in Town - A Rising Knight
About the game: Duck, Duckson's father, takes him to Town, capital of the Duck Kingdom and home of the Duck King. Duckson wants to become the greatest Duck Knight ever. To fullfill his dream, he must explore a peculiar town, full of mysteries and weird places, meet a bunch of quirky villagers and prove that he is worth the title. Duck in Town - A Rising Knight is the first chapter in this series of comedy 3D graphic adventure games, heavily inspired by the classics of the genre. Features Explore Town, capital of the Duck Kingdom Enjoy an unique story full of funny dialogs Join the Duck Guild Play as a cute duck Discover the mysteries of the recent Pigeon War Win the squawk contest Did I mention ducks?
